==English==

===Etymology===
From ''[[north]]'' + ''[[-ward]]''

===Noun===
'''northward'''

# The [[direction]] or [[area]] lying to the north of a place.

===Adjective===
'''northward'''

# Situated or directed towards the north; moving or facing towards the north.

====Derived terms====
*[[northwardly]]
*[[northwards]]

===Adverb===
'''northward'''

# Towards the north; in a northerly direction.

